<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-2">Architecture</h2>
<p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 mb-4">The video pipeline is designed for a worker-based backend architecture:</p>
<pre><code>API Server
 ├── /api/video/generate       ← accepts prompt, queues job
 ├── /api/video/:id/status     ← poll render progress
 └── /api/video/:id/result     ← download final video

Workers (Queue)
 ├── prompt-expand-worker      ← LLM prompt enrichment
 ├── scene-plan-worker         ← LLM scene decomposition
 ├── image-worker              ← keyframe generation (DALL·E, Nano Banana)
 ├── video-worker              ← video synthesis (Kling 2.5, Runway)
 └── render-worker             ← FFmpeg stitch + multi-format export

Storage (S3 / R2 / MinIO)
 └── projects/{id}/            ← keyframes, clips, final video, metadata</code></pre>

